t time in a hundred years.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aCommunismzSoviet Union. 7aHISTORY / Revolutionary.2bisacsh1 aKellogg, Paul, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMelentyeva, Mariya, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311127214608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2022z978311127419540uhttps://doi.org/10.15215/aupress/9781771992732.0140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781771992749423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781771992749/original  a978-3-11-127214-6  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-127419-5  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2022b2022  aGBV-deGruyter-alles